  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6466684">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6466684/" class="title-link">写本好的科普书就这么困难吗？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6466684"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/80856381/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/80856381/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">[已注销]</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-12-18"
      class="main-meta">2013-12-18 16:24:39</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6466684_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  在买书之前我特地上网上看了一下评论，无论是豆瓣还是亚马逊，上面的评价都不怎么好。但是我思索再三，毕竟国内关于航母的入门书籍一共也没有几本，除了它就只有房兵的《大国航母》了。最终我还是选择了把《百年航母》和《大国航母》一起买下来，两本对比着看。《百年航母》已...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6466684/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6466684_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6466684_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










